{{champion:114}}

just a dumb, poorly designed champion. never falls behind because of her %HP true damage, she becomes impossible to 1v1 once she gets ravenous because of her stupid ult heal zone, free crits, and even if you manage to catch her with all her dashing she just blocks whatver cc you use and stuns you

if you pick a squishy she can kill you, if you pick a tank she just ults you and runs around in a circle dealing uncounterable damage and then gets her fucking stupid heal zone you have to disengage from (giving her more time to smack you with %HP true damage), her laning phase is binary as hell because she just q's onto your vitals and runs away while getting a heal too, since her q prioritizes everything and does all the work for her, you can just aim it in the general direction of a champion and it will hit your vital
